What is the output of the following code?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int x = 0;

if (x != 0 &amp;&amp; 10 / x &gt; 1)
{
    System.out.println(&quot;Valid&quot;);
}
else
{
    System.out.println(&quot;Invalid&quot;);
}</code></pre></div>

How many times does System.out.print("*"); execute?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>for (int i = 1; i <= 3; i++)
{
    for (int j = i; j <= 3; j++)
    {
        System.out.print("*");
    }
}</code></pre></div>

Which value is printed?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int a = 5;
int b = 10;
System.out.println((a > b) ? (a - b) : ((b > 2 * a) ? b : a));</code></pre></div>

What is the output after the code snippet executes?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>for (int i = 0; i <= 5; i++)
{
    if (i == 2)
        continue;
    if (i == 4)
        break;
    System.out.print(i + " ");
}</code></pre></div>

What is the output?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int x = 7;

if (x > 5)
{
    if (x < 10 && x % 2 == 1)
{
        System.out.println("Odd and in range");
    }
}</code></pre></div>

What is the output of the following code segment?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int x = 5;
int y = 7;
if (x > 5)
{
    y = 10;
}
else if (x >= 5)
{
    y = 20;
}
else if (y > 10)
{
    y = 30;
}
System.out.println(y);</code></pre></div>

What is the final value of count after the following code segment executes?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int count = 0;
int limit = 5;
while (limit > 0)
{
    limit -= 2;
    count++;
}</code></pre></div>

What is printed by the following code segment?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>String s = "";
for (int i = 1; i < 5; i++)
{
    s += i;
}
System.out.println(s);</code></pre></div>

What is the output of the following code segment?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int sum = 0;
for (int k = 1; k <= 10; k++)
{
    if (k % 4 == 0)
        break;
    sum += k;
}
System.out.println(sum);</code></pre></div>

What is the final value of the variable output after the following code segment executes?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>String output = "";
for (int i = 1; i <= 4; i++)
{
    for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++)
    {
        if (i + j > 5)
        {
            break;
        }
        output += "(" + i + "," + j + ")";
    }
}</code></pre></div>

What is the output of the following code segment?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int p = 10;
int q = 2;
while (p > q)
{
    if (p % 3 == 0)
    {
        p--;
    }
    else
    {
        p -= q;
        q++;
    }
}
System.out.println(q);</code></pre></div>

What is the final value of the variable sum after the following code segment executes?<div class="card p-3 mt-2"><pre class="m-0"><code>int sum = 0;
for (int i = 10; i >= 0; i -= 3)
{
    if (i == 4)
    {
        continue;
    }
    if (i < 5)
    {
        sum += 1;
    }
    else
    {
        sum += 2;
    }
}</code></pre></div>
